        "title": "Clear Browser's Cache",
        "excerpt":"If you have trouble accessing the Quire on your web browswer, you can try clearing the browser’s cache.   Chrome   Step 1: At the top right, click on the More options icon and hover to More tools.      Step 2: Click on Clear browsing data.      Step 3: Make sure Cached images and file is checked, and click on the Clear Data button.      Step 4: Press Ctrl + Shift + R (or ⌘ + Shift +R for Mac) to refresh the page.  ","categories": ["clear","browser","cache"],
