        "title": "Merge Two Quire Accounts",
        "excerpt":"When you forget that you have already created a Quire account with a personal email. After using Quire with your work email, you would like to merge both accounts together.   Step 1: Grant the email A (the one you want to keep) to be admin of all the projects/organizations created by email B.   Step 2: Login in as A and remove the permission of the other one B (the one you don’t want).   Step 3: Delete B account.   Step 4: Add email B as the second email to the account associated with email A in the Account Settings.      Step 5: Both accounts with email A can also be accessed with email B.  ","categories": ["merge","2","Quire","accounts"],
